<div class="row">
  <br><br><br>
  <div class="medium-8 medium-centered column">
    <p>I look forward to speaking with you. Please answer three questions and  you will be taken to the calendar to schedule a conversation. â€“ Dr. Fletcher</p>
  </div>
  <form >
      <div class="medium-8 medium-centered column">
              <label>Name:
                <input ng-model="connect.name" type="text" required/>
              </label>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered">
        <label>What is your expertise?</label>
        <textarea  ng-model="connect.expertise" cols="30" rows="6" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered">
       <label>How can I be of service to you?</label>
        <textarea ng-model="connect.service"  cols="30" rows="6" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered">
        <label>How can we collaborate?</label>
        <textarea ng-model="connect.collaborate" cols="30" rows="6" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered" style="text-align: center;">
        <button type="submit"   ng-click="sendConnectEmail(connect)">Take me to the Calendar</button>
      </div>
    </form>
</div>